cacheResource.documentation:
Caches the given resource
* `file` Path to the resource
@return Succeed to cache the resource asked

fromJSON.documentation:
Parses the given file as JSON
* `file` File to parse
@return Object created

releaseResource.documentation:
Releases the given resource
* `file` Path to the resource
@return Succeed to release the resource specified

getGlobal.documentation:
Fetches the value associated with the given key in the global space
* `key` Key to look for
@return Value found

getPath.documentation:
Converts the path to an usable path
* `file` User given path
@return Null<String> Path to use or null if invalid

getShared.documentation:
Fetches the value associated with the given key in the shared space
* `key` Key to look for
@return Value found
